## Dry-run -> Apply -> Rollback

The runner (`scripts/evolve/migrate-apply.mjs`) interprets the structured `steps[]`
above with snapshot-based rollback. Dry-run writes nothing; apply snapshots →
forwards → verifies (auto-rollback + halt on failure); rollback restores the
snapshot / inverts the moves. Idempotent: re-running with nothing to do is a no-op.
